no.ntnu.stud.ubilearn.parse

Class SyncContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.ntnu.stud.ubilearn.parse.SyncContent

  • public class SyncContent
extends java.lang.Object
    SyncContent is the applications access point to Parse (our BaaS). It only contains static methods, and as such it is not intended to be initialised. Because of a-sync calls and data dependencies throughout the system, it is not recommended to change call sequence of the different methods.
